    dc:description "FIGURES 10–13. E. andrematosi sp. nov., habitus. 10–11 Male, holotype (IBSP 124323) (10 dorsal, 11 ventral); 12–13 Female, paratype (IBSP 62064) (12 dorsal, 13 ventral). Scale lines: 2 mm." ;
